SWAT TxtInOut inputs

Source: R/datasets.R
swat_txtinout_data.Rd

Named list that mirrors a SWAT TxtInOut directory from the example project.

Usage

swat_txtinout_data

Format

Named list of character vectors. Each element is the content of one SWAT input file (e.g., file.cio, .gw, pcp*.pcp).

Source

Prepared by the hydroSWAT authors.

See also

Other Data: example_basin_datasets, gridded_climate_netcdfs, qobserved, riv1, subs1

Examples

str(swat_txtinout_data[1:3])

The value for PND_FR should be"| __truncated__ "           5.000    | PND_PSA: Surface area of ponds when filled to principal spillway [ha]" ...
